@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About Us</PageTitle>

<div class="about-container">
    <section class="about-hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>About Our Company</h1>
            <p class="lead">Empowering businesses through innovation and excellence since 2008</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-story">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <div class="story-grid">
                <div class="story-text">
                    <h2>Our Story</h2>
                    <p>Founded with a vision to transform how businesses operate in the digital age, we've grown from a small startup to a trusted partner for hundreds of companies worldwide.</p>
                    <p>Our journey has been marked by continuous innovation, unwavering commitment to quality, and a deep understanding of our clients' needs. Every solution we create is built on years of expertise and a passion for excellence.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="story-image">
                    <div class="image-placeholder">
                        <img src="images/about_1.jpg" alt="Our Story"/>
                        @* <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="120" height="120" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"></path>
                            <polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"></polyline>
                            <line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
                        </svg> *@
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-what-we-do">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <h2>What We Do</h2>
            <p class="section-intro">As a specialized software agency, we leverage cutting-edge .NET technologies to transform how businesses operate and compete in the digital landscape.</p>

            <div class="services-grid">
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"></path>
                            <polyline points="7.5 4.21 12 6.81 16.5 4.21"></polyline>
                            <polyline points="7.5 19.79 7.5 14.6 3 12"></polyline>
                            <polyline points="21 12 16.5 14.6 16.5 19.79"></polyline>
                            <polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"></polyline>
                            <line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>.NET Technology Expertise</h3>
                    <p>We specialize in building robust, scalable applications using the latest .NET technologies—from Blazor and ASP.NET Core to Azure cloud services. Our deep expertise ensures your solutions are built on a solid, future-proof foundation.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline>
                            <polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Legacy System Modernization</h3>
                    <p>Transform outdated systems into modern, efficient applications. We breathe new life into legacy code, migrating to current technologies while preserving your critical business logic and ensuring zero disruption to operations.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                            <path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Custom Software Development</h3>
                    <p>Your business is unique—your software should be too. We design and build tailored solutions that perfectly fit your specific workflows, requirements, and goals, eliminating the compromises of off-the-shelf software.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M12 20v-6M6 20V10M18 20V4"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Performance & Maintainability</h3>
                    <p>We optimize your applications for speed, reliability, and long-term maintainability. Through code refactoring, architecture improvements, and best practices, we ensure your software runs efficiently and evolves with your business.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M18 10h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 9 20h9a5 5 0 0 0 0-10z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Cloud-Based Solutions</h3>
                    <p>Leverage the power of cloud computing with our Azure-based solutions. We help you migrate to the cloud, build cloud-native applications, and optimize your infrastructure for scalability, security, and cost-efficiency while ensuring seamless integration with your existing systems.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"></polyline>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Automation & Reporting</h3>
                    <p>Streamline your operations with intelligent automation and real‑time insights. We design custom workflows and reporting systems that eliminate manual tasks, reduce errors, and give you clear visibility into the metrics that matter. From automating routine processes to building dashboards that drive smarter decisions, we help your business run faster, leaner, and more confidently.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="tech-stack">
                <h3>Our Technology Stack</h3>
                <div class="tech-badges">
                    <span class="tech-badge">.NET 10</span>
                    <span class="tech-badge">Blazor</span>
                    <span class="tech-badge">ASP.NET Core</span>
                    <span class="tech-badge">Azure</span>
                    <span class="tech-badge">Azure AI</span>
                    <span class="tech-badge">C#</span>
                    <span class="tech-badge">Entity Framework</span>
                    <span class="tech-badge">SQL Server</span>
                    <span class="tech-badge">REST APIs</span>
                    <span class="tech-badge">OpenAI</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-mission">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="mission-statement">To deliver innovative solutions that drive measurable results, empower teams, and create lasting value for our clients and their customers.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-values">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <div class="values-grid">
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"></path>
                            <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"></path>
                            <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Innovation</h3>
                    <p>We constantly push boundaries and explore new technologies to stay ahead of the curve.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
                            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
                            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
                            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Collaboration</h3>
                    <p>We believe in the power of teamwork and building strong partnerships with our clients.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Excellence</h3>
                    <p>We are committed to delivering the highest quality in everything we do.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Integrity</h3>
                    <p>We operate with transparency, honesty, and accountability in all our relationships.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    @* Commented out until team grows - uncomment when you have additional employees
    <section class="about-team">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <h2>Our Team</h2>
            <p class="team-intro">We're a diverse group of passionate professionals dedicated to helping you succeed.</p>
            <div class="team-stats">
                <div class="stat">
                    <div class="stat-number">50+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Team Members</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat">
                    <div class="stat-number">20+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Countries Represented</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat">
                    <div class="stat-number">15+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Years Average Experience</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    *@

    <section class="about-cta">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <h2>Ready to Work Together?</h2>
            <p>Let's discuss how we can help transform your business.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

